Package: ggPMX
Title: PMX ggplot2-based tool to facilitate diagnostic plots for NLME models
Description: A ggplot2-based tool to facilitate diagnostic plots for NLME
    models. You provide your model data, you tell ggPMX reader how to map variables, 
    ggPMX will take care of the generating all diagnotic plots for you or  a single report.
Version: 0.9.9.9-6
